sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.HAS_EXAMS = "Y" AND COURSEalias0.HAS_PROJECTS = "Y" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER > 299 ;
